nodes.text: Star Wars Adventures 5 is the fifth issue of the Star Wars Adventures comic series. The comic was written by Katie Cook and Casey Gilly, illustrated by Cara McGee and Ethan Beavers, and was released by IDW Publishing on June 23, 2021.

Padme [sic] and Anakin have grand plans to have a romantic night celebrating a recent victory. But before they get a chance to get together, Anakin is Jedi-napped by a group of outlaws with their sights on a holocron in the Jedi temple! Now it's up to Padme to use all of her cunning to infiltrate the outlaw base and rescue him.
